  <summary>Jellyfin client focused on music</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Gelly is a Jellyfin Media Server client focused specifically on music playback.
      Simply connect to a Jellyfin server and listen to your entire library!
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Browse your music collection by artist or album</li>
      <li>Modern GTK/Adwaita interface with MPRIS support</li>
      <li>Written in Rust</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
